text: Buzan-pristan () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Seitovsky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 473 as of 2010. There are 13 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Buzan River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Buzan-pristan
